              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12211495559302900941">During their full acquaintance, Darcy writes secret letters to Elizabeth. However, he doesn&apos;t send them. They are signed, sealed and addressed and hidden. In this story, those hidden letters are accidentally mailed and Elizabeth receives them unbeknownst by her family or others. The letters and some humility by all parties lead to a wonderful happily ever after.</span>
  <span id="freeText12211495559302900941" style="display:none">During their full acquaintance, Darcy writes secret letters to Elizabeth. However, he doesn't send them. They are signed, sealed and addressed and hidden. In this story, those hidden letters are accidentally mailed and Elizabeth receives them unbeknownst by her family or others. The letters and some humility by all parties lead to a wonderful happily ever after.</span>
